        <div class="color-bar__icon color-bar__icon--blue "></div> 
        <h3 class="h-c-headline h-c-headline--two color-bar__quote"> <span>The results are incredible, it actually helped us transform our whole vision. </span> <span class="color-bar__highlight color-bar__highlight--blue">We want to be a global brand. Google Marketing Platform facilitates that growth.</span> </h3> 
        <p class="color-bar__credit"> <span class="color-bar__author">Martijn van der Zee</span>, Chief Digital Officer, Rituals </p> 
